Should've listened to the lady, Johnny.

26
00:01:31,093 --> 00:01:32,097
Thump.

27
00:01:39,109 --> 00:01:40,120
We've got him, Batman.

28
00:01:42,110 --> 00:01:43,088
'That's a broom closet.'

29
00:01:43,112 --> 00:01:45,090
There's no way..

30
00:01:45,114 --> 00:01:46,115
Out?

