And then we wanna see you saw a lady in half.

44
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:50,219
There won't be any encore performances tonight.

45
00:03:50,243 --> 00:03:52,229
And what makes you so sure?

46
00:03:52,253 --> 00:03:55,213
Because this time, it's two against one.

47
00:03:55,237 --> 00:03:56,221
Piece of cake.

48
00:03:56,245 --> 00:03:58,241
Numbers can be deceiving.

49
00:03:59,243 --> 00:04:00,263
And so can I.

50
00:04:01,242 --> 00:04:02,222
Two of 'em?

51
00:04:02,246 --> 00:04:04,252
So it would seem. Split up.

52
00:04:11,253 --> 00:04:16,265
Thwack.

53
00:04:28,278 --> 00:04:29,261
Huh! Unh!

54
00:04:29,285 --> 00:04:31,271
'Oh, Batman.'

55
00:04:43,303 --> 00:04:44,304
beep

56
00:04:48,293 --> 00:04:49,294
whoosh.

57
00:04:53,316 --> 00:04:57,301
My broom theory's sounding better all the time.

58
00:05:00,318 --> 00:05:02,289
I know he took the paintings off the wall

