Master Bruce, have you been at this all night?

62
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:21,299
So, any luck?

63
00:05:21,323 --> 00:05:23,320
I recovered a hair sample from the museum security station

64
00:05:23,344 --> 00:05:26,310
