No. I've known John for years.

69
00:05:34,357 --> 00:05:35,358
He's a good man.

70
00:05:36,337 --> 00:05:37,378
And has the perfect alibi.

71
00:05:38,338 --> 00:05:41,329
He was saved from the villain by the Batman himself.

72
00:05:41,353 --> 00:05:43,330
