You gotta admit that two men would explain

75
00:05:46,364 --> 00:05:49,345
all that strangeness at the museum.

76
00:05:49,369 --> 00:05:51,345
Well, some of it, anyway.

77
00:05:51,369 --> 00:05:53,338
