81
00:06:00,374 --> 00:06:02,348
Let's revisit the crime scenes.

82
00:06:02,372 --> 00:06:05,371
There has to be something we've missed.

83
00:06:11,381 --> 00:06:15,358
Ding Bruce, what brings you by?

84
00:06:15,382 --> 00:06:16,372
In all the excitement the other night

85
00:06:16,396 --> 00:06:19,378
I never did get a chance to admire your collection.

86
00:06:19,402 --> 00:06:23,379
Come on. We both know that's not why you're here.

87
00:06:23,403 --> 00:06:25,374
Who can resist a mystery?

88
00:06:25,398 --> 00:06:27,379
You wanna see the closet for yourself.

89
00:06:27,403 --> 00:06:29,392
Guilty as charged.

90
00:06:30,403 --> 00:06:31,412
Be my guest.

91
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:41,394
'Readings are coming in, Master Bruce.'

92
00:06:41,418 --> 00:06:43,425
Interesting, we're picking up traces

