00:06:50,416 --> 00:06:52,407
the same radioactivity at the museum

96
00:06:52,431 --> 00:06:56,431
'on the mysteriously reappeared stolen paintings.'

97
00:07:00,436 --> 00:07:02,411
Thanks for indulging me, John.

98
00:07:02,435 --> 00:07:04,402
Not a problem.

99
00:07:04,426 --> 00:07:05,424
Closet aside, I do have an ulterior motive

100
00:07:05,448 --> 00:07:07,414
