00:14:47,910 --> 00:14:50,897
'Find the bat. Exterminate it.'

231
00:14:52,893 --> 00:14:55,902
whoosh whoosh whoosh.

232
00:14:56,905 --> 00:14:57,920
When all is said and done

233
00:14:58,899 --> 00:15:00,897
he is but one man, but we..

234
00:15:00,921 --> 00:15:03,912
We are an army.

235
00:15:08,913 --> 00:15:10,896
'Batman's been spotted by the atrium.'

236
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:12,931
'All Everywhere Men to the atrium.'

237
00:15:15,924 --> 00:15:16,926
slam

238
00:15:22,941 --> 00:15:23,944
clang

239
00:15:41,951 --> 00:15:43,946
thump thump thump.

240
00:15:47,965 --> 00:15:50,934
Oh, come now, Batman.

