242
00:15:52,965 --> 00:15:55,945
'It hardly matters how many of me you break.'

243
00:15:55,969 --> 00:15:56,979
'I'll just make more.'

244
00:15:57,958 --> 00:15:58,965
boom boom boom.

245
00:16:06,976 --> 00:16:08,951
