265
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:32,040
Oh, it's worse than that, Johnny.

266
00:17:32,064 --> 00:17:34,060
Your duplicates are unstable.

267
00:17:35,061 --> 00:17:37,073
One solid punch, and poof.

268
00:17:40,075 --> 00:17:42,050
That's it. It's dead.

269
00:17:42,074 --> 00:17:44,059
- We're on our own. - Suits me.

270
00:17:44,083 --> 00:17:47,066
Never was much good at long division.

