273
00:18:10,111 --> 00:18:13,101
We've just run out of reinforcements.

274
00:18:16,113 --> 00:18:18,075
Let go of me.

275
00:18:18,099 --> 00:18:19,091
Quiet, Johnny boy.

276
00:18:19,115 --> 00:18:23,087
Batman may not know it, but the battle's over.

277
00:18:23,111 --> 00:18:25,115
'It's only a matter of time.'

278
00:18:27,115 --> 00:18:30,093
Did you hear that? It's only a matter of time.

279
00:18:30,117 --> 00:18:32,090
Before you're toast.

280
00:18:32,114 --> 00:18:34,102
And before you've outlived your usefulness.

281
00:18:34,126 --> 00:18:36,112
What's copy number one gonna do with so many of you?

282
00:18:36,136 --> 00:18:38,139
'Where could he hide a few hundred Marlowes?'

283
00:18:39,118 --> 00:18:40,117
'And how could he stand the competition?'

284
00:18:40,141 --> 00:18:42,104
'When the fighting's done'

285
00:18:42,128 --> 00:18:45,108
'he'll recall each and every one of you.'

286
00:18:45,132 --> 00:18:48,108
You'll all cease to exist.

287
00:18:48,132 --> 00:18:49,126
What if the Batman's right?

288
00:18:49,150 --> 00:18:52,124
Don't listen to him. Keep fighting.

289
00:18:52,148 --> 00:18:56,121
Hey, think about it. If we win this, we're toast.

290
00:18:56,145 --> 00:18:59,118
Shut up, you traitor!

291
00:18:59,142 --> 00:19:01,124
If one of us survives, we all do.

292
00:19:01,148 --> 00:19:04,130
Then you won't mind if I'm the one surviving.

293
00:19:04,154 --> 00:19:07,132
The Quantex.. As long as he has it, none of us are safe.

294
00:19:07,156 --> 00:19:09,136
You're playing right into his hand.

295
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,134
Don't worry. We'll protect you.

296
00:19:11,158 --> 00:19:12,174
But they all look alike.

297
00:19:13,153 --> 00:19:16,176
How will you know who's with you and who's against you?

298
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:20,151
Quiet. You want him to recall all of us?

299
00:19:20,175 --> 00:19:23,146
Now that's a plan.

300
00:19:23,170 --> 00:19:25,155
I'll get it. Get the Quantex!

301
00:19:25,179 --> 00:19:27,165
We can't let him use it.

302
00:19:27,189 --> 00:19:29,184
No. Stop.

303
00:19:30,182 --> 00:19:32,172
Don't make me do it.

304
00:19:34,196 --> 00:19:39,185
Beep poof poof poof.

305
00:19:41,182 --> 00:19:42,183
Huh?

306
00:19:44,199 --> 00:19:46,167
You haven't won yet, Batman.

307
00:19:46,191 --> 00:19:48,182
Two against one. Piece of cake.

308
00:19:48,206 --> 00:19:50,211
I'll create another army of Everywhere Men.

309
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:52,180
With the same result.

310
00:19:52,204 --> 00:19:54,188
Then I'll recall it and start over

311
00:19:54,212 --> 00:19:56,186
as many times as I have to.

312
00:19:56,210 --> 00:19:58,213
Eventually you'll fall.

313
00:19:59,215 --> 00:20:01,221
Will you please shut up?

314
00:20:08,209 --> 00:20:10,202
'I thought I could help people everywhere'

315
00:20:10,226 --> 00:20:14,222
but all I am is... Nowhere Man.

316
00:20:15,236 --> 00:20:17,203
'John, it's great of you'

317
00:20:17,227 --> 00:20:19,216
'to donate your entire collection to the museum.'

318
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:21,206
'It seemed like the right thing to do'

319
00:20:21,230 --> 00:20:22,391
'after everything I've done.'

320
00:20:23,222 --> 00:20:25,217
But, John, you didn't do anything.

321
00:20:25,241 --> 00:20:29,214
Perhaps, but part of me always wanted to be

322
00:20:29,238 --> 00:20:33,215
more like that other Marlowe.. Confident, cool..

323
00:20:33,239 --> 00:20:34,230
Maybe it's a good thing that the only place

324
00:20:34,254 --> 00:20:37,217
I've ever been comfortable is inside my shell.

325
00:20:37,241 --> 00:20:40,241
Any room in that shell for one more?

326
00:20:45,245 --> 00:20:48,239
Johnny, you've spent too much time locked away

327
00:20:48,263 --> 00:20:51,244
with your art collection and science projects.

328
00:20:51,268 --> 00:20:53,242
Stay out here with..

329
00:20:53,266 --> 00:20:55,254
With you?

330
00:21:14,277 --> 00:21:16,295
Screech vroom

331
00:21:22,287 --> 00:21:23,304
whoosh

